query:
INSERT INTO event_seating_config (
            event_id,
            has_seating,
            allow_unspecified_seat,
            unspecified_seat_label
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
        ON CONFLICT (event_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            has_seating = $2,
            allow_unspecified_seat = $3,
            unspecified_seat_label = $4,
            last_modified = NOW()
        RETURNING
            event_id,
            has_seating,
            allow_unspecified_seat,
            unspecified_seat_label,
            created_at,
            last_modified
